# UI Design System — Design Tokens

## Visual Identity

**Cinematic dark marketing** (Artlist-style reference): pure black canvas, **electric gold** (`#e8c547`) as primary brand/CTA, warm radial glows (amber / soft red) in heroes, large rounded cards, glass panels, optional **display serif** (`font-display`, Cormorant Garamond via `next/font` on `<html>`).

- Body copy and UI: geometric sans (system / default sans stack).
- Major headings (landing sections): `font-display` + `font-semibold` … `font-bold` as needed.

---

## Token Definition — `src/styles/global.css`

Tailwind v4 `@theme` registers tokens as **utility classes**.
Use `:root` for rgba values and gradients (cannot go in `@theme`).

**Live source of truth** — always read `global.css` for exact hex; the table below summarizes intent:

| Role | Token / variable | Tailwind examples |
|------|------------------|-------------------|
| Page background | `--color-page` (#000) | `bg-page` |
| Card / panel | `--color-surface`, `--color-elevated` | `bg-surface`, `bg-elevated` |
| Brand / CTA gold | `--color-brand`, `--color-brand-light`, `--color-brand-dim` | `bg-brand`, `text-brand-light` |
| Secondary warm accent | `--color-accent` | `text-accent`, `bg-accent/10` |
| Text | `--color-foreground`, `--color-muted`, `--color-subtle` | `text-foreground`, `text-muted` |
| Text on gold buttons | `--color-inverse` | `text-inverse` |
| Display font stack | `--font-display` | `font-display` |
| Hero mesh | `--gradient-hero` | `style={{ background: 'var(--gradient-hero)' }}` |
| CTA fill | `--gradient-cta` | same pattern when not using solid `bg-brand` |
| Gradient text | `--gradient-text` | `GradientText` or `bg-clip-text` + variable |
| Navbar scrim | `--color-bg-overlay` | `style={{ background: 'var(--color-bg-overlay)' }}` |

**Opacity / borders** — use Tailwind `/` syntax: `border-white/8`, `border-brand/25`, `bg-white/3`.

**Marketing glow on headings** — utility class `text-glow-heading` (soft gold/white bloom).

**Glass panels** — class `glass` (`backdrop-blur` + translucent fill + hairline border).

---

## Common components (reuse, do not reinvent)

| Component | Path | Use for |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `CommonButton` | `@/components/common/CommonButton` | Pill marketing CTAs: `primary` (gold), `secondary` (white), `outline`, `ghost`. Wrap with `<Link>` for navigation. |
| `BrandLogo` | `@/components/common/BrandLogo` | Header/footer wordmark + gold mark. |
| `SectionHeader` | `@/components/common/SectionHeader` | Badge + `font-display` title + optional gradient span + subtitle + optional `action` slot. |
| `TagPill` | `@/components/common/TagPill` | Small uppercase genre/category chips on dark. |
| `MediaCard` | `@/components/common/MediaCard` | Rounded aspect-ratio frame + optional label/overlay. |
| `Badge` | `@/components/common/Badge` | Eyebrow / status pills. |
| `Card` | `@/components/common/Card` | Generic content cards. |

**HeroUI `Button`** — use inside app/dashboard forms and dense UI; **marketing landing CTAs** should prefer `CommonButton` for consistent gold pills.

