## Patterns

### Glass sticky header
```tsx
<header className="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/8 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl supports-backdrop-filter:bg-black/30">
```

### Page shell
```tsx
<div className="min-h-screen bg-page text-foreground">
```

### Hero with warm glow
```tsx
<section className="relative overflow-hidden bg-page">
  <div className="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" style={{ background: 'var(--gradient-hero)' }} />
  <div className="relative z-10">{/* … */}</div>
</section>
```

### Section title (serif)
```tsx
<h2 className="font-display text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
```

### Primary CTA
```tsx
<Link href="/sign-up" className="inline-flex">
  <CommonButton variant="primary" size="lg">…</CommonButton>
</Link>
```

### Glass floating panel
```tsx
<div className="glass rounded-card p-4 shadow-card">…</div>
```

### Equal-height card grid (e.g. "How it works" steps)
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-stretch lg:gap-6">
  <article className="flex h-full flex-col">
    <div className="flex h-full min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col rounded-card border border-white/10 bg-elevated/85 p-6 shadow-card">
      {/* content */}
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
```

---

## Typography

- Marketing headings: `font-display`, `tracking-tight`, `text-foreground`; avoid `font-extrabold` on serif — prefer `font-semibold` unless a block is sans-only.
- Body: `text-muted` for descriptions; meta / hints: `text-subtle`.
- Tight modern sans labels: `tracking-tight` or `tracking-widest` + `uppercase` for nav labels.

## Spacing & layout

- Content width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8` (or shared `Container`).
- Section vertical rhythm: `py-20 sm:py-28` (or `py-24 sm:py-32` for hero).
- Cards: `rounded-card`, `border-white/8` or `border-brand/20` for emphasis.

## Rules

- **Prefer theme tokens** (`bg-page`, `text-brand-light`, `border-white/6`) — no arbitrary hex in JSX.
- Use `style={{ }}` only for `var(--gradient-*)`, `var(--color-bg-overlay)`, and similar variables.
- Do not use bare `text-white` / `text-black` for theme text — use `text-foreground` / `text-inverse`.
- Gold glow (`shadow-cta`, `shadow-brand`) on primary CTAs and featured cards only; keep the rest restrained.
- Icons: always import from `lucide-react`. Do not inline SVG.
